   LIKE CallLimit.

DEF VAR lcDeliPara   AS CHAR NO-UNDO.
DEF VAR lcAlarmMess  AS CHAR NO-UNDO. 
DEF VAR liDefCLCust  AS INT  NO-UNDO.
